    • Caregiver

      public Caregiver(String firstName, String surname, String telephone, String username, String password, String locked)
      Constructor to initiate an object of class Patient with the given parameter. Use this constructor to initiate objects, which are not persisted yet, because it will not have a patient id (pid).
      Parameter:
      firstName - First name of the caregiver.
      surname - Last name of the caregiver.
